        }, {
            "line": "To advance in the game, you must show the correct evidence to a statement with the present button."
        }, {
            "line": "The present button is now enabled in the evidence window. Use it with our Aesop evidence!",
            "type": "examination",
            "denyPress": "true",
            "denyForward": "true",
